juniLocalAddressServerAgent.name: juniLocalAddressServerAgent

revisions.description: Added support for rsAddressSharedPoolTable, update agent to version 6.
Juniper-ADDRESS-POOL-MIB: Added support for address pool aliases.
Juniper-ADDRESS-POOL-MIB: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
Juniper-ADDRESS-POOL-MIB: Added support for address pools with multiple address ranges.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniLocalAddressServerAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Local Address Server component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniLocalAddressServerAgentV1.name: juniLocalAddressServerAgentV1
juniLocalAddressServerAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Local Address Server component of the JUNOSe SNMP
        agent.  This version of the Local Address Server component was supported
        in JUNOSe 1.3 thru 3.1 system releases.
juniLocalAddressServerAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the Local Address Server application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when pool exhaustion variables and notifications were added.

juniLocalAddressServerAgentV2.name: juniLocalAddressServerAgentV2
juniLocalAddressServerAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Local Address Server component of the JUNOSe SNMP
        agent.  This version of the Local Address Server component was supported
        in JUNOSe 3.2 system releases.
juniLocalAddressServerAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the Local Address Server application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for address pools with multiple address ranges.

juniLocalAddressServerAgentV3.name: juniLocalAddressServerAgentV3
juniLocalAddressServerAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the Local Address Server component of the JUNOSe SNMP
        agent.  This version of the Local Address Server component was supported
        in JUNOSe 3.3 thru 5.2 system releases.
juniLocalAddressServerAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the Local Address Server application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for address pool aliases.

juniLocalAddressServerAgentV4.name: juniLocalAddressServerAgentV4
juniLocalAddressServerAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the Local Address Server component of the JUNOSe SNMP
        agent.  This version of the Local Address Server component is supported
        in JUNOSe 5.3 and subsequent system releases.
juniLocalAddressServerAgentV4.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the Local Address Server application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for next PoolProfile index.

juniLocalAddressServerAgentV5.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the Local Address Server application in JUNOSe.
